10. Broader Insight

A key realization during development:

AI may allow many technically minded pilots to prototype avionics systems.

Historically this required large engineering resources.

Lowering the barrier to prototyping may lead to:

many more experiments

community innovation

improvements in flight safety

This project may serve as an early demonstration of that possibility.

